{"tid":2224691,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華舒福　留給你　查辛祖　誰帶路","createTime":"2020-09-30T16:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T12:52:11.000Z","uid":35348,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de910744b9b00d20c879d9639f082584287d71ac","tid":2224691,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"　 活華特舊日伴隨自己　Fake news通處飛<br />\n　 活華特膽敢預言自己　簽一堆有機<br />\n　 但到一定年紀　經不起英超起飛<br />\n　 放下碌J　喜中帶悲<br />\n<br />\n　 曼聯奪大熱漸成歷史　彷彿一世紀<br />\n　 蘇斯克查運舊時夢想　晶宮中跌死<br />\n　 為了股價而放棄　要奮鬥來盡厚利<br />\n　 世界是活華遊戲　那買入傳言誰謹記<br />\n<br />\n　 華舒福　留給你　查辛祖　誰帶路<br />\n　 轉會窗給你再做　問你又會否出價更高<br />\n　 林加德　留給你　誰歡笑　誰憤怒<br />\n　 想當初買人無數　轉會有太多變數<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在&nbsp;※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=079650f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網&nbsp;"},{"pid":"7b78e8fdd57ad7d1a350647f853a2d7635acd5f1","tid":2224691,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b645aeb1df3d37d7b271318a86e1d39f464e27a","tid":2224691,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b78e8fdd57ad7d1a350647f853a2d7635acd5f1","tid":2224691,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4544b87f88b1f736b35675c5e70a5d1e9b365caa","tid":2224691,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b645aeb1df3d37d7b271318a86e1d39f464e27a","tid":2224691,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b78e8fdd57ad7d1a350647f853a2d7635acd5f1","tid":2224691,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16: